description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Chukcha purrs with a rating of 60, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 300, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 5 for East, 1 for South, and Stringalong for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30605-85171-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [300 Votes, Hall of Fame]
